  "commit_message": "feat(pnpr): server-accelerated installs via pnprServer (endpoints + client + CLI) (#12077)\n\n## What\n\nAdds an opt-in **`pnprServer`** setting that offloads the slow part of an install — dependency resolution and computing which files the local store is missing — to a [pnpr](https://github.com/pnpm/pnpm/tree/main/pnpr) server, which streams back only the missing files. `node_modules` is still linked **locally** from the server-produced lockfile (like server-side rendering: the compute runs remotel",
